# System Design

## Overview

The system follows a lightweight hybrid memory architecture designed for:
- low latency
- offline processing
- scalable conversational memory
- efficient retrieval

The architecture combines:
- local conversational memory
- compressed checkpoint summaries
- lightweight synchronization
- contradiction-aware retrieval

